There is only one campus of Namal Institute,which is located at 30KM Mianwali Talagang Road. It is a 90 minute drive from motorway through Balkasar interchange near Chakwal city.
There are four 4-years undergraduate degree programs being offered at Namal Institute, i.e. B.S. Electrical Engineering, B.S. Computer Science, B.S. Mathematics and BBA.
